NUC7i3BNB, add it to the blacklist.

Buglink: https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1520902
Signed-off-by: Hans de Goede <hdegoede@redhat.com>
Signed-off-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

